            "title": "A股向上   深股升0.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早段向好，高開後升幅擴大。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3519點，升3點或0.09%，現報3522，升6點或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10902，升29點或0.27%，現報10929，升56點或0.51%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報4039，升5點或0.12%，現報4049，升15點或0.39%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數開報2279，升10點或0.44%，現報2289點，升20點0.89%。</p>\n</div>",
